<section class="about-content">
  <div class="about-wrap">
    <div class="about-story reveal">
      <h2>Why I <span class="serif">do this</span></h2>
      <p>I started doing this because I was tired of seeing great local businesses held back by terrible websites. A master barber with 15 years of experience shouldn't be losing customers to a competitor with a better Wix template. A nail artist doing incredible work shouldn't be invisible on Google because their site loads in 6 seconds. I use the same technology stack that powers billion-dollar startups — Astro, Vercel, modern CSS — and package it into a service that local business owners can actually afford. The result: sites that load in under a second, rank on Google, and turn visitors into bookings.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-diff">
      <h2 class="reveal">What makes me <span class="serif">different</span></h2>
      <div class="diff-grid stagger">
        <div class="reveal diff-card">
          <h3>Speed as a Feature</h3>
          <p>My sites average 0.3 second load times. WordPress averages 4.2 seconds. That difference means more visitors stay, more bookings happen, and Google ranks you higher.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal diff-card">
          <h3>No Monthly Website Tax</h3>
          <p>Most agencies charge $200-500/month for hosting a slow WordPress site. My hosting costs are near-zero because sites are static and served from a CDN.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal diff-card">
          <h3>Built to Rank</h3>
          <p>Perfect Lighthouse scores, semantic HTML, structured data, and local SEO optimization aren't add-ons — they're built into every site from day one.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal diff-card">
          <h3>Real Design, Not Templates</h3>
          <p>While I use a curated template library for efficiency, every site is customized to your brand. Your customers will think it was designed from scratch.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  .about-content{padding:60px 24px 120px}.about-wrap{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto}
  .about-story{margin-bottom:64px}.about-story h2{font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.4rem);letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:20px}
  .about-story p{font-size:16px;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.85}
  .about-diff h2{font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.4rem);letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:32px}
  .diff-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:16px}@media(max-width:768px){.diff-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .diff-card{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:28px 24px}
  .diff-card h3{font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px}.diff-card p{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.7}
</style>
